 more damage to our country. Up to now, there has been a one way cherry-picking of information by the federal government to support the notion of keeping marijuana illegal, while at the same time information indicating the benefits of Legalization are not presented by the government when it is obvious that these benefits do exist.</div><br />	phaxel	49	54	5	1	http://opengov.ideascale.com/akira/dtd/3740-4049	
